 <div class=article-intro id=content>


 <h1>R 语言基础</h1>
<p>一门新的语言学习一般是从输出 "Hello, World!" 程序开始，R 语言的 "Hello, World!" 程序代码如下：</p>
<div class=example>
<h2 class=example>实例（helloworld.R）</h2>
<div class=example_code>
myString <span style=color:#170>&lt;-</span> <span style=color:#a11>"Hello, World!"</span><br>
<br>
<span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>print</span> <span style=color:#080>(</span> myString <span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
</div>
<br><a target=_blank href="https://www.runoob.com/try/runcode.php?filename=helloworld&amp;type=r" class=showbtn rel="noopener noreferrer">运行实例 »</a>
</div><p>

以上实例将字符串 "Hello, World!" 赋值给 myString 变量，然后使用 print() 函数输出。</p>

<p><strong>注意：</strong>R 语言赋值使用的是左箭头 <span class=marked>&lt;-</span> 符号，不过一些新版本也支持等号 <strong>=</strong>。</p>

<h3>变量</h3>
<p>R 语言的有效的变量名称由字母，数字以及点号 <span class=marked>.</span> 或下划线 <span class=marked>_</span> 组成。 </p>
<p>变量名称以字母或点开头。</p>
<table class=reference>
<tbody><tr>
<th>变量名</th>
<th>是否正确</th>
<th>原因</th>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>var_name2.</td>
<td>正确</td>
<td>字符开头，并由字母、数字、下划线和点号组成</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>var_name%</td>
<td>错误</td>
<td>% 是非法字符</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>2var_name</td>
<td>错误</td>
<td>不能数字开头</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td><p>.var_name,</p>
<p>var.name</p></td>
<td>正确</td>
<td>可以 . 号开头，但是要注意 . 号开头后面不能跟着数字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>.2var_name</td>
<td>错误</td>
<td>. 号开头后面不能跟着数字</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>_var_name</td>
<td>错误</td>
<td>不能以下划线 _ 开头</td>
</tr> 
</table>
<h3>变量赋值</h3>
<p>
最新版本的 R 语言的赋值可以使用左箭头 <span class=marked>&lt;-</span>、等号 <span class=marked>=</span> 、右箭头 <span class=marked>-&gt;</span> 赋值:</p>
<div class=example><h2 class=example>实例</h2> <div class=example_code>
<span style=color:#a50># 使用等号 = 号赋值</span><br>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> var.1 <span style=color:#170>=</span> <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>c</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#a11>0</span>,<span style=color:#a11>1</span>,<span style=color:#a11>2</span>,<span style=color:#a11>3</span><span style=color:#080>)</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; <br>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>print</span><span style=color:#080>(</span>var.1<span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
<span style=color:#080>[</span><span style=color:#a11>1</span><span style=color:#080>]</span> <span style=color:#a11>0</span> <span style=color:#a11>1</span> <span style=color:#a11>2</span> <span style=color:#a11>3</span><br>
<br>
<span style=color:#a50># 使用左箭头 &lt;-赋值</span><br>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> var.2 <span style=color:#170>&lt;-</span> <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>c</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#a11>"learn"</span>,<span style=color:#a11>"R"</span><span style=color:#080>)</span> &nbsp; <br>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>print</span><span style=color:#080>(</span>var.2<span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
<span style=color:#080>[</span><span style=color:#a11>1</span><span style=color:#080>]</span> <span style=color:#a11>"learn"</span> <span style=color:#a11>"R"</span><br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; <br>
<span style=color:#a50># 使用右箭头 -&gt; 赋值</span><br>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>c</span><span style=color:#080>(</span>TRUE,<span style=color:#a11>1</span><span style=color:#080>)</span> <span style=color:#170>-&gt;</span> var.3<br>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>print</span><span style=color:#080>(</span>var.3<span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
<span style=color:#080>[</span><span style=color:#a11>1</span><span style=color:#080>]</span> <span style=color:#a11>1</span> <span style=color:#a11>1</span> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<br>
</div></div>
<p>查看已定义的变量可以使用 <strong>ls()</strong> 函数：</p>
<div class=example><h2 class=example>实例</h2> <div class=example_code>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>print</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>ls</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#080>)</span><span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
<span style=color:#080>[</span><span style=color:#a11>1</span><span style=color:#080>]</span> <span style=color:#a11>"var.1"</span> <span style=color:#a11>"var.2"</span> <span style=color:#a11>"var.3"</span><br>
</div></div>
<p>删除变量可以使用 <strong>rm()</strong> 函数：</p>
<div class=example><h2 class=example>实例</h2> <div class=example_code>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>rm</span><span style=color:#080>(</span>var.3<span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>print</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>ls</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#080>)</span><span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
<span style=color:#080>[</span><span style=color:#a11>1</span><span style=color:#080>]</span> <span style=color:#a11>"var.1"</span> <span style=color:#a11>"var.2"</span><br>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> <br>
</div></div>
<p>上一章节中我们已经学会来如何安装 R 的编程环境，接下来我们将为大家介绍 R 语言的交互式编程与文件脚本编程。</p>
<h3>交互式编程</h3>
<p>我们只需要在命令行中执行 <span class=marked>R</span> 命令就可以进入交互式的编程窗口：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pln>R</span></pre>
<p>执行完这个命令后会调出 R 语言的解释器，我们在 &gt; 符后面输入代码即可。</p>
<p><img width=70% src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"></p>
<p>
交互式命令可以通过输入 <span class=marked>q()</span> 来退出：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pun>&gt;</span><span class=pln> q</span><span class=pun>()</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=typ>Save</span><span class=pln> workspace image</span><span class=pun>?</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=pln>y</span><span class=pun>/</span><span class=pln>n</span><span class=pun>/</span><span class=pln>c</span><span class=pun>]:</span><span class=pln> y</span></pre>
<p><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"></p>
<h3>文件脚本</h3>
<p>R 语言文件后缀为 <span class=marked>.R</span>。</p>
<p>接下来我们创建一个 runoob-test.R 文件：代码如下：</p>
<div class=example><h2 class=example>runoob-test.R 文件</h2> <div class=example_code>
myString <span style=color:#170>&lt;-</span> <span style=color:#a11>"RUNOOB"</span><br>
<br>
<span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>print</span> <span style=color:#080>(</span> myString <span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
</div></div><p>

接下来我们在命令行窗口使用 Rscript 来执行该脚本：</p>

<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=typ>Rscript</span><span class=pln> runoob</span><span class=pun>-</span><span class=pln>test</span><span class=pun>.</span><span class=pln>R</span></pre>
<p>输出结果如下：<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=str>"RUNOOB"</span></pre>
<p><img src="data:image/jpeg;base64,"></p>
<hr><h2>输入输出</h2>
<h3>print() 输出</h3>
<p><span class=marked>print()</span> 是 R 语言的输出函数。</p>
<p>和其他编程语言一样，R 语言支持数字、字符等输出。<p>输出的语句十分简单：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=kwd>print</span><span class=pun>(</span><span class=str>"RUNOOB"</span><span class=pun>)</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=kwd>print</span><span class=pun>(</span><span class=lit>123</span><span class=pun>)</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=kwd>print</span><span class=pun>(</span><span class=lit>3e2</span><span class=pun>)</span></pre>
<p>执行结果：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=str>"RUNOOB"</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>123</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>300</span></pre>
<p>R 语言与 node.js 和 Python 一样，是解释型的语言，所以我们往往可以像使用命令行一样使用 R 语言。<p>如果我们在一行上进输入一个值，那么 R 也会把它直接标准化输出：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pun>&gt;</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>5e-2</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>0.05</span></pre>
<h3>cat() 函数</h3>
<p>如果需要输出结果的拼接，我们可以使用 <span class=marked>cat()</span> 函数：</p>
<div class=example><h2 class=example>实例</h2> <div class=example_code>
<span style=color:#170>&gt;</span> <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>cat</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#a11>1</span>, <span style=color:#a11>"加"</span>, <span style=color:#a11>1</span>, <span style=color:#a11>"等于"</span>, <span style=color:#a11>2</span>, <span style=color:#a11>'<span style=color:#000099;font-weight:bold>\n</span>'</span><span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
<span style=color:#a11>1</span> 加 <span style=color:#a11>1</span> 等于 <span style=color:#a11>2</span> <br>
</div></div>
<p>
<span class=marked>cat()</span> 函数会在每两个拼接元素之间自动加上空格。</p>
<h3>输出内容到文件</h3><p>
R 语言输出到文件的方法十分多样，而且很方便。</p>
<p>
<span class=marked>cat()</span> 函数支持直接输出结果到文件：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pln>cat</span><span class=pun>(</span><span class=str>"RUNOOB"</span><span class=pun>,</span><span class=pln> file</span><span class=pun>=</span><span class=str>"/Users/runoob/runoob-test/r_test.txt"</span><span class=pun>)</span></pre>
<p>这个语句不会在控制台产生结果，而是把 "RUNOOB" 输出到 "/Users/runoob/runoob-test/r_test.txt" 文件中去。</p>
<p>file 参数可以是绝对路径或相对路径，建议使用绝对路径，Windows 路径格式为 <span class=marked>D:\\r_test.txt</span>。</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pln>cat</span><span class=pun>(</span><span class=str>"RUNOOB"</span><span class=pun>,</span><span class=pln> file</span><span class=pun>=</span><span class=str>"D:\\r_test.txt"</span><span class=pun>)</span></pre>
<p>注意：这个操作是"覆盖写入"操作，请谨慎使用，因为它会将输出文件的原有数据清除。如果想"追加写入"，请不要忘记设置 append 参数：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pln>cat</span><span class=pun>(</span><span class=str>"GOOGLE"</span><span class=pun>,</span><span class=pln> file</span><span class=pun>=</span><span class=str>"/Users/runoob/runoob-test/r_test.txt"</span><span class=pun>,</span><span class=pln> append</span><span class=pun>=</span><span class=pln>TRUE</span><span class=pun>)</span></pre>
<p>执行以上代码后，打开 r_test.txt 文件内容如下：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pln>RUNOOBGOOGLE</span></pre>
<h3>sink()</h3>
<p>sink() 函数可以把控制台输出的文字直接输出到文件中去：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pln>sink</span><span class=pun>(</span><span class=str>"/Users/runoob/runoob-test/r_test.txt"</span><span class=pun>)</span></pre><p>
这条语句执行以后，任何控制台上的输出都会被写入到 "/Users/runoob/runoob-test/r_test.txt" 文件中去，控制台将不会显示输出。</p>
<p>注意：这个操作也是"覆盖写入"操作，会直接清除原有的文件内容。</p>
<p>如果我们依然像保留控制台的输出，可以设置 split 属性：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pln>sink</span><span class=pun>(</span><span class=str>"/Users/runoob/runoob-test/r_test.txt"</span><span class=pun>,</span><span class=pln> split</span><span class=pun>=</span><span class=pln>TRUE</span><span class=pun>)</span></pre>
<p>如果想取消输出到文件，可以调用无参数的 sink ：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pln>sink</span><span class=pun>()</span></pre>
<div class=example><h2 class=example>实例</h2> <div class=example_code>
<span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>sink</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#a11>"r_test.txt"</span>, <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>split</span><span style=color:#170>=</span>TRUE<span style=color:#080>)</span> &nbsp;<span style=color:#a50># 控制台同样输出</span><br>
<span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>for</span> <span style=color:#080>(</span>i <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>in</span> <span style=color:#a11>1</span><span style=color:#170>:</span><span style=color:#a11>5</span><span style=color:#080>)</span> <br>
&nbsp; &nbsp; <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>print</span><span style=color:#080>(</span>i<span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
<span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>sink</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#080>)</span> &nbsp; <span style=color:#a50># 取消输出到文件</span><br>
<br>
<span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>sink</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#a11>"r_test.txt"</span>, <span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>append</span><span style=color:#170>=</span>TRUE<span style=color:#080>)</span> <span style=color:#a50># 控制台不输出，追加写入文件</span><br>
<span style=color:#05a;font-weight:bold>print</span><span style=color:#080>(</span><span style=color:#a11>"RUNOOB"</span><span style=color:#080>)</span><br>
</div></div> 
<p>执行以上代码，当前目录下会生存一个 r_test.txt 文件，打开文件内容如下：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>2</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>3</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>4</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>5</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=str>"RUNOOB"</span></pre>
<p>控制台输出为：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>2</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>3</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>4</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=lit>5</span></pre>
<h3>文字输入</h3>
<p>可能我们会联想到 C 语言中的 scanf 、Java 中的 java.util.Scanner，如果你学习过 Python 可能对 input() 函数更熟悉。但是 R 语言本身作为一种解释型的语言，更类似于一些终端脚本语言（比如 bash 或者 PowerShell），这些语言是基于命令系统的，本身就需要输入和输出且不适合开发面向用户的应用程序（因为他们本身就是给最终用户使用的）。因此 R 语言没有专门再从控制台读取的函数，文字输入在 R 的使用中一直在进行。</p>
<h3>从文件读入文字</h3>
<p>R 语言中有丰富的文件读取函数，但是如果纯粹的想将某个文件中的内容读取为字符串，可以使用 readLines 函数：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pln>readLines</span><span class=pun>(</span><span class=str>"/Users/runoob/runoob-test/r_test.txt"</span><span class=pun>)</span></pre>
<p>执行结果：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=str>"RUNOOBGOOGLE"</span></pre>
<p>读取结果是两个字符串，分别是所读取的文件包含的两行内容。</p>
<blockquote><p><strong>注意：</strong>所读取的文本文件每一行 (包括最后一行) 的结束必须有换行符，否则会报错。</p></blockquote>
<h3>其他方式</h3>
<p>除了文字的简单输入输出以外，R 还提供了很多输入数据和输出数据的方法，R 语言最方便的地方就是可以将数据结构直接保存到文件中去，而且支持保存为 CSV、Excel 表格等形式，并且支持直接地读取。这对于数学研究者来说无疑是非常方便的。但是这些功能对于 R 语言的学习影响不大，我们将在之后的章节提到。</p>
<h3>工作目录</h3><p>
对于文件操作，我们需要设置文件的路径，R 语言可以通过以下两个行数来获取和设置当前的工作目录：</p>
<ul><li>
<strong>getwd()</strong> : 获取当前工作目录<li>
<strong>setwd()</strong> : 设置当前工作目录</ul>
<div class=example><h2 class=example>实例</h2> <div class=example_code>
<span style=color:#666666;font-style:italic># 当前工作目录</span><br>
print<span style=color:#7a0874;font-weight:bold>(</span>getwd<span style=color:#7a0874;font-weight:bold>(</span><span style=color:#7a0874;font-weight:bold>)</span><span style=color:#7a0874;font-weight:bold>)</span><br>
<br>
<span style=color:#666666;font-style:italic># 设置当前工作目录</span><br>
setwd<span style=color:#7a0874;font-weight:bold>(</span><span style=color:#a10>"/Users/runoob/runoob-test2"</span><span style=color:#7a0874;font-weight:bold>)</span><br>
<br>
<span style=color:#666666;font-style:italic># 查看当前工作目录</span><br>
print<span style=color:#7a0874;font-weight:bold>(</span>getwd<span style=color:#7a0874;font-weight:bold>(</span><span style=color:#7a0874;font-weight:bold>)</span><span style=color:#7a0874;font-weight:bold>)</span><br>
</div></div>
<p>执行以上代码输出结果为：</p>
<pre class="prettyprint prettyprinted"><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=str>"/Users/runoob/runoob-test"</span><span class=pln>
</span><span class=pun>[</span><span class=lit>1</span><span class=pun>]</span><span class=pln> </span><span class=str>"/Users/tianqixin/runoob-test2"</span></pre> 


 </div>

 </div>
